snippet.textDisplay: This might be a LONG shot but hello my name is Jasel Hudson. I’m messaging in regards to a beautiful family whom just suffered the loss of their very own home. Robert and Martha West are a married couple with 4 beautiful children 1 of them being in heaven now. All their children have a very unique story. Christian (pnutt) is “9 years old” and has battled heart problems since he was a baby. He’s has multiple surgeries and is a miracle baby. Matthew is “8 years old” and suffers from a special needs disability. He also has a speech disability but he’s a very awesome kid let me tell you. Sophia is “3 years old” and suffers from autism. She goes to multiple therapies and has learned sign language to help her communicate. Andrew whom is now in heaven passed away right before his due date. We all took his passing very hard. Robert and Martha were not the same after facing this loss but for the sake of their other children they remained strong. Robert is such a dedicated father and does everything he can to support his family. He works full time and spends the rest of his time taking care of his children. Martha is one amazing supportive mother. She’s a stay-at-home mom and dedicates all her time to taking the kids to school, dr appointments, and therapies while baby sitting her 3 other nieces and nephew. Believe me it may not seem like a lot but it really is. Her calendar stays filled up almost everyday. They’re such a humble loving family that really come from nothing. They spread so much love to the other families on their street. They always want to help everybody but never ask for anything in return.
